Localization.Name: Navoi Boots and Pants Shale
Localization.Description: Carrying Capacity: 0.4K µSCU\n\nBe ready to take on whatever the day brings when wearing the Navoi. This unique piece integrates the pants perfectly into knee high boots. Made from a combination of synthetic materials to be tough yet comfortable, the Navoi also comes with shin pads and pouches strapped onto each leg.
